abstract: >
  This repository contains a four-year analysis of NFL quarterback decision-making 
  using the Decision Efficiency Index (DEI), a new composite metric that evaluates 
  decision effectiveness, tempo, EPA impact, touchdowns, and turnover tendencies. 
  The project uses nflverse play-by-play data, Next Gen Stats, and a full Merit America 
  6-step analysis framework.